book, by Tom Badgett and Corey Sandler, targets both the multimedia
neophyte and experienced user. Written with an emphsis on business,
training, and education. $29.95 for paperback/CD-ROM set.

*Peterson's Register of Higher Education. This who's who of higher
education is the fully revised seventh edition offering a complete
listing of higher education's influential leaders and decision makers.
$49.95. For info: 1-800-338-3292.

